  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm trying to figure out where I stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] What other people-- what the people did, I think I said that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well, one of the most unpleasant thing in Mauritius was really malaria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And lots during the first couple of months, I think maybe at least 1/4 of all the people on Mauritius had gotten malaria at least one time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was extremely unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had mosquito nets, but you still had to be outside, and the mosquitoes just got to you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And malaria is a very unpleasant illness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I myself, I think I said it already, I had it about 13 times, which was really quite bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was in and out of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one time, I was particularly sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- after-- I had a different kind of mosquito, which gave you-- or not mosquito, but a different kind of virus, which gave you the malaria.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this was worse than the others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after I was finished with the malaria, I got jaundice and I was in the hospital for about two months.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think I lost probably 30 pounds during that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was really ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But after that, I somehow-- it got a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They tried-- when people were really ill, so they tried to get them some recreational facilities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Not recreational, but somehow-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] now I'm lacking a word again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Just after-- after an illness--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some-- some recovery-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] helping recovery places.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
